dct_title_s: Fifth map, or, Map of 1733 : to accompany Willard's History of the United States
dct_description_sm: Covers the Atlantic Coast of North America from Nova Scotia to Florida. Shows route of General Oglethorpe, 1733, and Palatines from Germany sent by Queen Ann, 1708. Appears in Emma Willard's History of the United States, or Republic of America, 1829 ed. Includes ill. "Genl. Oglethorpe with a colony commences the settlement of Georgia, 1733."
